售两方面产生显著提振作用，拥有城中村改造经验、当地资源丰富的地方国企有望率先受益。一线城市首例！广州探索房票安置政策，业内认为「未来北上深推广房票政策存在可能性」 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-acb1f9af538ce84b7fe2846707d6814b_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628486874"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyPWb8cao/bleEAMaCTEwMTk0MjQyMCD2s4GqBjAAOJcBQCJyCTYyODQ4Njg3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1698805092.655989", "card_id": "Q_627556689", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当你和自家宠物对视的时候，你在想什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-93e6c596f8ecde0db1f367a5b16dadd6_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627556689"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyPWb8cao/bleEAMaCTEwMTczNTg0OSC4rN2pBjAAOGBAI3IJNjI3NTU2Njg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1698805092.656224", "card_id": "Q_624404065", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「没有自我」和「无我」的区别是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这个问题自己想了很久，似乎明白又似乎不明白，麻烦神通广大的知友们各抒己见。 补充一下： 「没有自我」是我看心理学问题时想到的，「没有自我」会产生很多问题，比如爱抑郁、低自尊之类的。那么「无我」呢？ 它们肯定不一样吧？但我又参悟不了。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624404065"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyPWb8cao/bleEAMaCTEwMTAzNTY3NCCJieGoBjAAOIwCQCRyCTYyNDQwNDA2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "